{"sgc":false,"sfy":false,"qfy":false,"transUser":{"id":2354726,"status":99,"demand":1,"userid":116345109,"nickname":"Novachy","uptime":1523588832669},"lyricUser":{"id":56500,"status":99,"demand":0,"userid":256716226,"nickname":"byeHara","uptime":1523588832669},"lrc":{"version":20,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Whiteacre, Anastasia Laura\"}]}\n{\"t\":1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Whiteacre, Anastasia Laura\"}]}\n[00:11.17]Every day is a blur\n[00:14.57]Sometimes I can't tell what day it is\n[00:18.48]Don't know what day it is\n[00:20.74]Can you tell me what day it is?\n[00:23.80]Life's passing by\n[00:27.14]'Cause I'm out chasing empty highs\n[00:30.59]Every hello just means goodbye\n[00:33.44]But I'm looking for more this time\n[00:36.84]Can we start to slow it down?\n[00:40.55]Can we learn to live right now?\n[00:43.59]I just want to feel it all\n[00:49.31]I'm a Ferrari pulled off on Mulholland Drive\n[00:55.60]Over the city, the lights are so pretty from up here\n[01:01.51]I'm a Ferrari and after the party is done\n[01:07.83]I keep on going, missing the moments\n[01:12.20]Living in the fast lane is getting kind of lonely (yeah)\n[01:16.72]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh\n[01:20.31]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh-ooh\n[01:23.49]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh\n[01:25.99]Living in the fast lane is getting kind of lonely\n[01:29.28]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh\n[01:33.08]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh-ooh\n[01:36.15]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh\n[01:38.56]Living in the fast lane is getting kind of lonely\n[01:43.70]Got a heavy heart\n[01:46.39]'Cause it's still beating on its own\n[01:50.25]Might be going out in the crowd\n[01:53.58]But I'm still coming home alone\n[01:56.42]Not trying to say I'm not grateful for everything\n[02:03.01]I'm just going too fast to see\n[02:05.91]All the good things in front of me\n[02:09.27]I'm a Ferrari pulled off on Mulholland Drive\n[02:15.41]Over the city, the lights are so pretty from up here\n[02:21.62]I'm a Ferrari and after the party is done\n[02:27.74]I keep on going, missing the moments\n[02:31.99]Living in the fast lane is getting kind of lonely\n[02:35.67]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh\n[02:38.98]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh-ooh\n[02:41.93]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh\n[02:44.41]Living in the fast lane is getting kind of lonely\n[02:48.06]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh\n[02:51.47]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh-ooh\n[02:54.44]Whoo, ooh, ooh-ooh\n[02:59.37]I'm a Ferrari pulled off on Mulholland Drive\n[03:05.71]Over the city, the lights are so pretty from up here\n[03:12.00]I'm a Ferrari and after the party is done\n[03:18.03]I keep on going, missing the moments\n[03:22.12]Living in the fast lane is getting kind of lonely\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":9,"lyric":"[by:Novachy]\n[00:11.17]每天都过得浑浑噩噩\n[00:14.57]有时我分不清今天是什么日子\n[00:18.48]不知今夕何夕\n[00:20.74]你能告诉我今天是几月几号吗?\n[00:23.80]生命不断流逝着\n[00:27.14]因为我忙于追逐虚无的欢愉\n[00:30.59]每一声\"你好\"其实就意味着\"再见\"\n[00:33.44]但我这次却期许得到更多\n[00:36.84]我们能否试着放慢脚步?\n[00:40.55]我们能否学会活在当下?\n[00:43.59]我只想好好感受生命中的点点滴滴\n[00:49.31]我就像一辆停泊在穆赫兰大道上的法拉利\n[00:55.60]从这里放眼望去 撒满整座城市的光辉是如此迷人\n[01:01.51]当派对散席后 我化作一辆法拉利离场\n[01:07.83]我不断向前 同时留恋着那些片刻须臾\n[01:12.20]在快车道上过着人生 是有那么些孤独\n[01:16.72]\n[01:20.31]\n[01:23.49]\n[01:25.99]生活节奏太快是会有点寂寞\n[01:29.28]\n[01:33.08]\n[01:36.15]\n[01:38.56]在快车道上过着人生 是有那么些孤独\n[01:43.70]负荷着一颗沉沉的心脏\n[01:46.39]因为它总是兀自跳动着\n[01:50.25]也许会来到喧哗的人群里\n[01:53.58]但我仍然独自回到家中\n[01:56.42]并不是说我内心未存一丝感激\n[02:03.01]我只是走得太快了\n[02:05.91]以至于我忽视了眼前一切美好的事物\n[02:09.27]我就像一辆停泊在穆赫兰大道上的法拉利\n[02:15.41]从这里放眼望去 撒满整座城市的光辉是如此迷人\n[02:21.62]当派对散席后 我化作一辆法拉利离场\n[02:27.74]我不断向前 同时留恋着那些片刻须臾\n[02:31.99]生活节奏太快是会有点寂寞\n[02:35.67]\n[02:38.98]\n[02:41.93]\n[02:44.41]在快车道上过着人生 是有那么些孤独\n[02:48.06]\n[02:51.47]\n[02:54.44]\n[02:59.37]我就像一辆停泊在穆赫兰大道上的法拉利\n[03:05.71]从这里放眼望去 撒满整座城市的光辉是如此迷人\n[03:12.00]当派对散席后 我化作一辆法拉利离场\n[03:18.03]我不断向前 同时留恋着那些片刻须臾\n[03:22.12]在快车道上过着人生 是有那么些孤独\n"},"romalrc":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"yrc":{"version":16,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Whiteacre, Anastasia Laura\"}]}\n{\"t\":1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Whiteacre, An